        ('bb538f74-2229-4908-8ae1-c07b665ea3db', '2021-05-06', null, 'Revision to reported virus tests for England', 'Pillar 4 testing figures are reported for the UK as a whole. They were previously incorrectly included in figures for virus, PCR and antibody tests in England. 
