        ('ced1f2ac-4d7c-4b32-a772-413f4da50e09', '2021-04-17', null, 'Data for Wales no longer reported on Saturdays', 'As of the week commencing 12 April 2021, Public Health Wales have moved to a six day reporting period for  [COVID-19 surveillance](https://public.tableau.com/profile/public.health.wales.health.protection#!/vizhome/RapidCOVID-19virology-Public/Headlinesummary).  This means that there will be no reporting of the daily figures for Wales on Saturdays, and UK numbers have therefore only been updated  with data from England, Northern Ireland and Scotland.', 'Data for Wales reported on Sundays will be for the 24-hour period up to 9am on Friday, and data reported on Mondays will be for a 
