        ('d284c583-aec6-44b2-8625-1aee96e4beaf', '2021-09-17', null, 'Newly reported cases in Scotland reflects 24 hour period', 'The technical issues that prevented publication of cases for Scotland on 16 September 2021 are resolved. 

