        ('ca3fa793-b8e8-465c-86a2-aba37ae4ac86', '2021-04-30', null, 'Amendment to Northern Ireland vaccination numbers', 'Northern Ireland have switched to a new vaccinations management system (Northern Ireland Vaccinations Management System) 
