        ('e6cf06f2-7315-497c-bd8f-8bd26ea6661a', '2021-06-07', null, 'Vaccination uptake age demographics added for England', 'Vaccination uptake for England, shown by age group and for all adults, has been added. These are calculated for population surveillance purposes 
