        ('8e699397-8c24-4919-a24f-dd66a1d62157', '2021-06-02', null, 'Figures reported by Wales for 48-hour period', 'Figures reported on 1 June for Wales are for the 48-hour period from 9am Sunday 30 May to 9am Tuesday 1 June. The UK figures will also include 
