        ('44e91a25-b29c-4905-a083-ded1717ad20e', '2021-06-25', null, 'Potential under-reporting of cases in Scotland', 'Public Health Scotland (PHS) are investigating a potential delay in laboratory processing of specimens in Lighthouse laboratories. 
