The cumulative number of deaths in each affected local authority and region will also change.

This improvement means that when there are conflicting resident addresses, the address noted at death registration will take precedence.
This will result in fewer changes to the geographical allocation of historical death counts in future.

Details of the changes in total number of deaths at local authority level for 16 June 2021 data are available 
to [download as CSV](/downloads/miscellaneous/change_in_death_allocations_in_England_2021-06-16.csv).', null, '52f2fd0a-a6ad-45b1-bb0b-2ed7c9933acf', false, false, null, '2021-06-16 12:09:43.783720'),
        ('d8b25fbb-7e38-448c-b12c-c994be4fcdd2', '2021-05-20', null, 'Revision to historical case data in England', 'The introduction of a new system disrupted the removal of cases where a positive rapid lateral flow test (LFD) was followed by all negative laboratory (PCR) tests taken within 3 days, as reported earlier this week.  Therefore a further 180 cases have been removed today.  Regions and local authorities do not show the actual number of new cases reported.  UK and England numbers of newly reported cases have been adjusted and correctly reflect new cases reported. This issue will be ongoing over the next few days.', null, '52f2fd0a-a6ad-45b1-bb0b-2ed7c9933acf', false, true, null, '2021-05-20 13:40:45.784504'),
        ('9828817f-4079-41fa-aa9d-e8356f9991fd', '2021-04-06', null, 'Cases and deaths reported for Wales cover 48 hour period', 'The UK numbers for cases and deaths contain a 48 hour reporting period for Wales, up to 9am Monday 5th April 2021', null, '52f2fd0a-a6ad-45b1-bb0b-2ed7c9933acf', false, true, null, '2021-04-06 13:56:25.785122'),
        ('22094824-f3ca-4201-9b75-d32502db834e', '2021-04-02', null, 'Revision to historical vaccination data in Scotland', 'Due to a problem with data flowing from GP systems, vaccination data for Scotland was incomplete for vaccines reported  on 27 to 30 March 2021. Numbers for the affected days have been revised.', null, '52f2fd0a-a6ad-45b1-bb0b-2ed7c9933acf', false, false, null, '2021-04-02 15:37:24.785428'),
        ('3b721461-172c-457b-abda-2f8ed1df8b44', '2021-03-30', null, 'No update to testing data', 'Due to testing data not being available for the whole of the UK, these metrics have not been updated.  They will be updated in the next release.', null, '52f2fd0a-a6ad-45b1-bb0b-2ed7c9933acf', false, true, null, '2021-03-30 12:54:03.785733'),
        ('b6265dd5-7bfb-42fa-a1c7-e8392f8b374b', '2021-03-25', null, 'Revision to Northern Ireland and UK historical vaccination counts', 'The Northern Ireland Department of Health has migrated to a single data management system for vaccinations, which has required  data reconciliation. Numbers of vaccinations given for 22 March 2021 and earlier have been revised for both Northern Ireland and the UK.', null, '52f2fd0a-a6ad-45b1-bb0b-2ed7c9933acf', false, false, null, '2021-03-25 13:10:34.786044'),
