        ('21062732-c338-4f00-8b47-ec7f835a3bc2', '2021-06-30', null, 'Vaccinations map launched', 'A map showing the percentage of adults vaccinated is now available under the **Interactive map** page.  The map visualises percentage uptake for dose 1 and dose 2 for upper and lower tier local authorities and Middle layer Super Output Areas (MSOAs).

