        ('21176de8-f646-4141-8b7f-fbd5a9cb51bc', '2021-03-22', null, 'New blog: how we expanded the dashboard', 'Our latest blog, [Behind the scenes: Expanding the COVID-19 dashboard](https://publichealthmatters.blog.gov.uk/2021/03/22/behind-the-scenes-expanding-the-covid-19-dashboard/) is available on
